data.name: label16.Text
data.value:
Only registered voters are allowed to participate.
Each voter is entitled to cast one vote only.
Log in using your assigned account credentials.
Voting is allowed only during the scheduled election period.
Use a reliable device when accessing the system.
Ensure you have a stable internet connection before voting.
Your vote is confidential and cannot be traced back to you.
Do not attempt to vote on behalf of another person.
Avoid refreshing or closing the browser while voting.
Once submitted, your vote cannot be changed.
Contact the election committee if you encounter technical issues.
Do not attempt to manipulate or interfere with the system.
Respect the voting process and fellow voters.
Wait for the official announcement of results after the election closes.
